252
00:17:37,199 --> 00:17:38,079
Stay away from him.

253
00:17:38,239 --> 00:17:38,959
Don't approach him.

254
00:17:39,719 --> 00:17:41,760
Brother Shuyu once told me that

255
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:44,000
