282
00:19:21,560 --> 00:19:22,359
Next time you go to the temple,

283
00:19:22,520 --> 00:19:23,680
you can give me another one.

284
00:19:23,959 --> 00:19:24,640
Take it.

285
00:19:25,359 --> 00:19:26,439
But after today,

286
00:19:26,599 --> 00:19:27,079
you don't know

287
